# Q-SYS Lua — Official Documentation

Q-SYS control scripts use **Q-SYS Lua (Script v2)**, not standard Lua. Before adding, changing, or refactoring any `.lua` file in this workspace, consult [Q-SYS Help](https://help.qsys.com) for the correct APIs, syntax, and limitations.

## Required behavior

- **Do not assume** standard Lua/stdlib features exist unless documented for Q-SYS.
- **Verify** APIs against help.qsys.com — especially `Component.*`, `Controls.*`, `Timer.*`, and event-handler patterns.
- **Match** existing project conventions in `.cursor/rules/qsys-lua-architecture.mdc` and `qsys-simple-lua-architecture.mdc` unless the official docs require otherwise.

