## Q-SYS-specific patterns (not generic Lua)

```lua
-- Named component access (requires Code Name + Script Access on the block)
local gain = Component.New("Main_Gain")
gain.gain.EventHandler = function(ctl)
    if gain.gain.Value > 0 then gain.mute.Boolean = true end
end

-- Script-defined controls on a Text Controller
Controls.compExample.EventHandler = function(ctl) ... end

-- Discovery
for _, comp in pairs(Component.GetComponents()) do ... end

-- Timers
local t = Timer.New()
```

**Control names with decimals** (v9.12+): escape the dot — e.g. `comp["31\\.5Hz.gain"]`.

## When unsure

Search or browse [help.qsys.com](https://help.qsys.com) for the component type, control property, or library before implementing. Prefer official examples over generic Lua patterns.
